Package: ngramrr
Title: A Simple and Quick ngram tokenizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: "Chung-hong Chan <chainsawtiney@gmail.com> [aut,cre]"
Description: A simple ngram tokenizer to be used with the tm package. A replacement of RWeka's NGramTokenizer with no rJava (and the heavyweight RWekajars) dependency.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT
LazyData: true
Imports: tau
Suggests: tm, testthat, magrittr